data.description: Are you currently feeling crowded in your home?  With neighbors not to close this 2 story home is over 3500 ft. and has 3 spacious bedrooms downstairs while the upstairs offers a large game room with an oversized bedroom. It even has two closet spaces in the primary bedroom. The private backyard is large enough to add an outdoor kitchen and have gatherings while the kitchen has been beautifully upgraded with plenty of cabinet space. The living room will be the perfect place to slow down and to relax in front of the fireplace.
